<br>
I don't really worry about carrying around loot.  You can always buy/quest weight reduction bags.  Stamina is important because of Hit Points.  Items with hitpoints are highly valued in EQ because they are worth it.  You wanna get as much Hit Points you can get and it'll save you from death from time to time.<br>
